Package: ecisr
Type: Package
Title: ecisr - Toolkit for processing Electrical Cell-Substrate Impedance Sensing Data
Version: 0.1.9000
Author: James Hucklesby
Maintainer: James Hucklesby <jhuc964@aucklanduni.ac.nz>
Description: Allows for the analyasis of ECIS code using the R enviroment. Includes tools for importing both the raw ECIS data in resampled form and modeled data generated by the ECIS package. Also includes some ggplot2 templates that allow for rapid generation of commonly used plots.
